</td></tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Be vigilant and strong. The Emperor knows what evil lurks in the vacillation of a weak fool.</b>
</td>
<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000_3rd_Edition_Rulebook" title="Warhammer 40,000 3rd Edition Rulebook">Warhammer 40,000 3rd Edition Rulebook</a>, page 49
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Better crippled in body than corrupt in mind.</b>
</td>
<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000:_Rogue_Trader" title="Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader">Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader</a>, page 182;<br />
<p><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000_3rd_Edition_Rulebook" title="Warhammer 40,000 3rd Edition Rulebook">Warhammer 40,000 3rd Edition Rulebook</a>, page 119
