</td></tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Brave are they who know everything yet fear nothing</b>
</td>
<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000_4th_Edition_Rulebook" title="Warhammer 40,000 4th Edition Rulebook">Warhammer 40,000 4th Edition Rulebook</a>, page 218
</td></tr>
<tr>
