</td>
<td align="center"><b>Burn the Heretic!</b><br />
<p><b>Kill the Mutant!</b><br />
<b>Purge the Unclean!</b>
</p>
</td>
<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000_4th_Edition_Rulebook" title="Warhammer 40,000 4th Edition Rulebook">Warhammer 40,000 4th Edition Rulebook</a>, page 68;<br />
