<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000:_Compendium" title="Warhammer 40,000: Compendium">Warhammer 40,000: Compendium</a>, page 85
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Consider the Predator. Let your soul be armoured with Faith, driven on the tracks of Obedience which overcomes all obstacles, and armed with the three great guns of Zeal, Duty and Purity.</b>
</td>
