<p><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000_5th_Edition_Rulebook" title="Warhammer 40,000 5th Edition Rulebook">Warhammer 40,000 5th Edition Rulebook</a>, page 95
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Even though you once called him friend, the Traitor has forsaken you. Show no mercy even if he begs it, for his soul is tainted and given the chance he will betray your trust.</b>
</td>
