</td>
<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Codex:_Black_Templars_(4th_Edition)" title="Codex: Black Templars (4th Edition)">Codex: Black Templars (4th Edition)</a>, page 9;<br />
<p><a href="/wiki/Warhammer_40,000_3rd_Edition_Rulebook" title="Warhammer 40,000 3rd Edition Rulebook">Warhammer 40,000 3rd Edition Rulebook</a>, page 96
</p>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Forgiveness is a sign of weakness.</b>
</td>
<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Codex:_Space_Marines_(4th_Edition)" title="Codex: Space Marines (4th Edition)">Codex: Space Marines (4th Edition)</a>, page 74
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">
</td>
<td align="center"><b>Forward Brothers, with loyalty to victory and glory!</b>
</td>
<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Imperial_Armour_Volume_Two_-_Space_Marines_and_Forces_of_the_Inquisition" title="Imperial Armour Volume Two - Space Marines and Forces of the Inquisition">Imperial Armour Volume Two - Space Marines and Forces of the Inquisition</a>, pg. 76
